{
  "text": "To prepare heart homogenates, first frozen hearts were pulverized at liquid N 2 temperature and then homogenized [CITATION_1] . Protein contents in homogenates were analyzed by using the Bradford method (Bio-Rad). Bovine serum albumin was used as a protein standard. Protein oxidation level in heart homogenates was determined as described previously [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
